description: Manual test case generation in structured JSON format
requirement: User should be able to log in using email and password.
prompt_used:
You are a senior QA engineer. Generate detailed manual test cases for the following requirement:

User should be able to log in using email and password.

Return the output **only in valid JSON** format (no explanations, no markdown). The JSON must be an array of objects, where each object has the following structure:

[
  {
    "test_case": "Unique ID or Title of the test case",
    "objective": "Purpose of this test case",
    "preconditions": ["Any preconditions required"],
    "test_data": ["List of test data items"],
    "test_steps": ["Step 1", "Step 2", "..."],
    "expected_results": ["Expected result 1", "Expected result 2"],
    "variations": ["Optional variations if any"],
    "edge_cases": ["Edge cases or negative tests"]
  }
]

⚠️ Important: Do not include any text outside of the JSON. Do not include markdown. Make sure it is valid JSON.

structured_test_cases.test_case: TC-001 - Login with Valid Email and Password
structured_test_cases.objective: Verify user can log in using email and password
preconditions: User has a registered account on the application
Email address is valid and not blocked
test_steps: Enter email address in the login form
Enter password in the login form
Click on the login button
Verify user is redirected to dashboard page
expected_results: User can log in successfully with valid credentials
Application redirects user to dashboard page after successful login

structured_test_cases.test_case: TC-002 - Login with Invalid Email and Password
structured_test_cases.objective: Verify application handles invalid email and password attempts
preconditions: User has a registered account on the application
test_steps: Enter invalid email address in the login form
Enter password in the login form
Click on the login button
Verify application displays error message for invalid credentials
expected_results: Application displays error message for invalid email and password combination
User cannot log in with invalid credentials

structured_test_cases.test_case: TC-003 - Login with Valid Email but Invalid Password
structured_test_cases.objective: Verify application handles valid email with invalid password attempts
preconditions: User has a registered account on the application
test_steps: Enter valid email address in the login form
Enter invalid password in the login form
Click on the login button
Verify application displays error message for invalid credentials
expected_results: Application displays error message for invalid password and valid email combination
User cannot log in with invalid password and valid email

structured_test_cases.objective: Verify application handles empty email attempts
preconditions: User has a registered account on the application
test_steps: Enter empty email address in the login form
Enter password in the login form
Click on the login button
Verify application displays error message for invalid credentials
expected_results: Application displays error message for empty email and valid password combination
User cannot log in with empty email and valid password

structured_test_cases.objective: Verify application handles empty password attempts
preconditions: User has a registered account on the application
test_steps: Enter email address in the login form
Enter empty password in the login form
Click on the login button
Verify application displays error message for invalid credentials
expected_results: Application displays error message for valid email and empty password combination
User cannot log in with valid email and empty password
